method_1 = Fill your bathtub with warm water (not hot) and add some children's bubble bath. Soak your baby for 15-20 minutes while you gently rub their skin. The water pressure helps reduce fever while the bubbles are soothing.
)item_2 = garlic tea
method_2 = Finely chop 2-3 cloves of garlic, add to boiling water, simmer for 5 minutes, cool slightly, and let your baby drink it through a spoon. The garlic helps break fever rapidly through natural anti-infectious properties.
urgent_advice = If you feel you're not able to handle this alone, panic, and call emergency services for help if necessary.
